column2: SELECT TOP #   p.petroMag_r,   p.petroMag_u,   s.ra,   s.dec,   p.lnLExp_r,   p.lnLDeV_r,   p.expAB_r,   p.expPhi_r,   p.deVAB_r,   p.deVPhi_r,   p.fracDeV_r,   s.class,   s.z,   s.zErr into mydb.MyTable from photoObj p JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID WHERE   s.class = &&& AND   s.z < # AND   p.lnLExp_r > lnLDeV_r
